{"tid":202964,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[10:28] 韋拿解釋神奇50碼笠射：「入球是向陳七致敬!」","createTime":"2017-04-16T02:30:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-17T05:07:14.000Z","uid":28938,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"456f2cf37381333f71ee5f817b4f07bf9d33c71d","tid":202964,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T02:30:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ioHsA05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FioHsA05.jpg&h=9d7dcf73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[10:28]昨日美職紐約城作客費城聯，紐約城射手韋拿於球賽末段離門五十多碼笠射入網，最後助紐約城贏2:0。賽後訪問中他解釋入球竟是向香港足球員陳七致敬!<br />\n<br />\n韋拿起初解釋因為疲倦不想再奔跑，因而決定大腳笠射入網。在眾記者懷疑此說法並再追問下，韋拿終於和盤托出：「好吧，這個入球其實是向陳七致敬的。」<br />\n<br />\n外國記者普遍不知道陳七是誰，韋拿進一步解釋：「記得有一年我來香港旅遊，順道低調地看了一場當地球會South China對英超熱刺的友誼賽。這場實力懸殊的比賽，我看到香港一名叫做陳七的球員於半場做出一記精采的笠射，『收死』熱刺門將，那個笠射無論從角度、技巧和視野而言，都是世界級的。」<br />\n<br />\n「他(陳七)是每個前鋒都追求的境界，自此以後我瘋狂搜集他的比賽片段，並模仿他的射門姿勢，終於在這場比賽成功做出這記笠射；當然，這個射門沒有陳七當時那個漂亮。」<br />\n<br />\n記者向陳七查詢此事，陳以短訊回應：「很多年前我說過：『韋拿踢法似我』，被傳媒認為我是大言不慚；現在我要再說一次：『韋拿踢法似我』。」<br />\n<br />\n韋拿係唔係講緊陳七呢球？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-ez0rQ5ZpKQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-ez0rQ5ZpKQ&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=49d2a7a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-ez0rQ5ZpKQ</a>"},{"pid":"b887e485ea7ede5a3bddc89b41c1817ffd300031","tid":202964,"uid":52524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T02:31:35.000Z","msg":"仲達<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"162fca835c795adb71a44c54ff840b396fe849b8","tid":202964,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T02:34:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲達<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n十年之後，終於發現陳七講既係真話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c70bc0db2f4fe63db7336520d04ca3355660b465","tid":202964,"uid":12587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T02:55:35.000Z","msg":"CHING ho ball"},{"pid":"52dffb2140c4fb412cb86056c24290d9414dcca9","tid":202964,"uid":43281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T03:00:07.000Z","msg":"有冇琴日入波果球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59085e651400b9a4e879ff37dbc09ecdb56ec15","tid":202964,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T03:09:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇琴日入波果球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tOSpLQNNdcs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DtOSpLQNNdcs&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=30c15636\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tOSpLQNNdcs</a><br />\n<br />\n比較下陳七果球靚d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef07d0dd5be6bf93b292dbe7bdb42915dedd7bbb","tid":202964,"uid":3296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T03:09:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9479218957c8bf7b701aedcecbfadf420cce486f","tid":202964,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:23:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>CHING ho ball</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n陳七好波"},{"pid":"4c000e3cd756508c330a2b3e5a57fea8948c29fd","tid":202964,"uid":101695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:33:36.000Z","msg":"陳七個球含金量高好多"},{"pid":"4a5c35e15faf9bd2376b37f7a3b30d8dff0a917f","tid":202964,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:35:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>陳七個球含金量高好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同意，如果陳七果時去西甲，就唔使年年都係C朗美斯咁悶了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c21d83242938aa1fcd0c2ea43d7a84f2a13d63fd","tid":202964,"uid":60785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:36:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad97644e6bf070b8cb800ac82335ac643b2a1104","tid":202964,"uid":54747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:51:24.000Z","msg":"韋拿仲未模仿到牙七講英文粗口既風範，唔夠努力牙👎🏻"},{"pid":"cd8bcc921415cd1675ca07a0b5ff310b956ee265","tid":202964,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:53:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>韋拿仲未模仿到牙七講英文粗口既風範，唔夠努力牙👎🏻</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n陳七從未唔講粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6348f9a22503868fa2616a76798ff1801753603b","tid":202964,"uid":29614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T05:02:42.000Z","msg":"連慶祝都要一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e617f2733c96b596ad35295066c1ffa564565e04","tid":202964,"uid":29742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T05:03:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ioHsA05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FioHsA05.jpg&h=9d7dcf73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[10:28]昨日美職紐約城作客費城聯，紐約城射手韋拿於球賽末段離門五十多碼笠射入網，最後助紐約城贏2:0。賽後訪問中他解釋入球竟是向香港足球員陳七致敬!<br />\n<br />\n韋拿起初解釋因為疲倦不想再奔跑，因而決定大腳笠射入網。在眾記者懷疑此說法並再追問下，韋拿終於和盤托出：「好吧，這個入球其實是向陳七致敬的。」<br />\n<br />\n外國記者普遍不知道陳七是誰，韋拿進一步解釋：「記得有一年我來香港旅遊，順道低調地看了一場當地球會South China對英超熱刺的友誼賽。這場實力懸殊的比賽，我看到香港一名叫做陳七的球員於半場做出一記精采的笠射，『收死』熱刺門將，那個笠射無論從角度、技巧和視野而言，都是世界級的。」<br />\n<br />\n「他(陳七)是每個前鋒都追求的境界，自此以後我